      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I test for STIs at home?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, there are many reputable at-home testing kits available. You typically collect a urine, swab, or small blood sample at home and mail it to a lab. These are convenient and discreet, though clinical testing is still the gold standard."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Does a standard checkup include STI testing?",
